metadata.name: The Awakening
metadata.description:
The world we live in always reminded us of the turmoil that has divided this world into two. But the greatest turmoil runs deep inside each person, conflicting between who we want to be and who we become. This feeling of uncertainty feeds us off from within, gradually leaving behind nothing but an incessant rage that's patiently sitting for its awakening.
